cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CG, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper presents a data structure for storing and querying a tree with color information, which is a problem in data structures (cs.DS) and computational geometry (cs.CG). The use of color information suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.AI) and pattern recognition (cs.LG). Finally, the succinctness of the data structure may also relate to data management (cs.DM).
